336
1346
00:47:39,685 --> 00:47:41,851
<i> Goo Joon Pyo</i>

337
1350
00:48:06,590 --> 00:48:07,858
Jan Di.

338
1354
00:48:09,360 --> 00:48:10,728
Woo Bin Sunbae.

339
1358
00:48:22,822 --> 00:48:24,809
