344
1378
00:48:38,189 --> 00:48:39,657
Don't worry too much.

345
1382
00:48:39,657 --> 00:48:40,992
It's nothing big.

346
1386
00:48:40,992 --> 00:48:43,260
He's just not allowed to go out.

347
1390
00:48:43,260 --> 00:48:47,098
