348
1394
00:48:47,098 --> 00:48:48,866
It'd be even weirder if nothing happened.

349
1398
00:48:51,235 --> 00:48:53,999
In any case, I was planning on going to see Joon Pyo.

350
1402
00:48:53,999 --> 00:48:55,946
Do you have any message you want me to pass on to him?

351
1406
00:48:59,647 --> 00:49:01,457
Jan Di, are you okay?

352
1410
00:49:02,399 --> 00:49:06,350
Ah!  As for me, well, I'm doing really well.

353
1414
00:49:08,746 --> 00:49:10,104
What?

354
1418
00:49:10,104 --> 00:49:11,422
Why are you looking at me like that?

355
1422
00:49:12,256 --> 00:49:13,157
Just because.

356
1426
00:49:13,891 --> 00:49:18,629
Living at Ji Hoo's house, both you and Ji Hoo look comfortable.

357
1430
00:49:19,883 --> 00:49:25,051
Geum Jan Di, Goo Joon Pyo, Yoon Ji Hoo. You three.

358
1434
00:49:25,051 --> 00:49:28,037
Whatever kind of fate it is...

359
1438
00:49:28,037 --> 00:49:30,641
it sure is complicated.

360
1442
00:49:30,641 --> 00:49:32,643
I'm just saying that's how it is.

361
1446
00:49:36,414 --> 00:49:37,848
Be strong, Geum Jan Di.

362
1450
00:49:39,349 --> 00:49:41,885
And thanks.

363
1454
00:49:41,885 --> 00:49:42,953
For what?

364
1458
00:49:43,587 --> 00:49:45,089
Ji Hoo.

365
1462
00:49:45,089 --> 00:49:48,359
I don't think I've ever seen him look so comfortable.

366
1466
00:49:49,126 --> 00:49:50,895
